\n但國泰o個d人好似唔係幾想<br />\n佢地淨係識驚，又唔行動<br />\n<br />\n你今日唔篤廿個人，聽日就俾人篤<br />\n<br />\n#篤灰challenge<br />\n<br />\n見到航空同公務員朋友，記得每日問佢：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「你今日篤左未呀？」</span><br />\n<br />\n公務員方面，上政府電話簿<br />\n<strong>[size=5]可以先針對政制及内地事務局同保安局<br />\no係得入面做o既，都唔方好得去邊<br />\n佢地好可能要成日去大陸<br />\n話俾中國知，佢地係暗黃[/size=6]</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:09:52.000Z","msg":"集思廣益  對付白色恐怖嘅方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506382\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506382</a>"},{"pid":"05f22b5fa1bcb7353383f6e26cc1f56d7c189640","tid":1515600,"uid":185990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"566a0abd62d0988c500a5498d58c4b6526587956","tid":1515600,"uid":251083,"like":218,"dislike":1,"score":217,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2MCU0H6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2MCU0H6.png&h=9835a0b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GJfrRPN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGJfrRPN.png&h=1900f37c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LdEsn8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LdEsn8.png&h=5928e1dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ne2RiuP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fne2RiuP.png&h=669999ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:10:02.000Z","msg":"集思廣益  對付白色恐怖嘅方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506382\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506382</a>"}]}